des: This briefing is to inform you of Lawrence, KS real estate listings, including the upcoming open houses that I will be hosting. New homes for sale, upcoming listings that have not hit the market yet so you can have first hand information and hopefully be the first one in the door. Interest rates and pertinent information to the local Lawrence, KS real estate market. There will also be helpful tips for homeowners like how to get your home ready to sell, or how to spruce up your property to be the best on the block.
